a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Name: ThinkPad X13/T14s Gen 1 AMD
a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Summary: Lenovo ThinkPad X13/T14s Gen 1 AMD System Firmware
a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Description:
This stable release fixes the following issues:

  • fix CPU frequency stuck issue
  • Fixed Out of order idle states under Linux.
  • Fix the issue[DFT187640]that the battery icon shows YB when the EUT(BIOS Setup Wake On LAN: AC Only) is woken up from SystemFullShutdown(AC)
  • Fix the issue[DFT179514]that EUT pop-up box "The connected AC adapter has a lower wattage than the recommended AC adapter which was shipped with the system..." after Pressing Power button with BIOS set Wake on LAN:AC and Battery.

Some new functionality has also been added:

  • update PIcode1004 to 1008

a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Name: ThinkPad X13/T14s Gen 1 AMD
a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Summary: Lenovo ThinkPad X13/T14s Gen 1 AMD System Firmware
a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Description:
This stable release fixes the following issues:

  • Optimize GPIO setting according to the newest GPIO table form EE in order to improve Linux S3 battery drain.

Some new functionality has also been added:

a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Name: ThinkPad X13/T14s Gen 1 AMD
a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Summary: Lenovo ThinkPad X13/T14s Gen 1 AMD System Firmware
a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Description: Included security issue update.&Modify AMD GPIO IRQ number for BSOD 0x133.&Add WA to fix LCD selftest issue.&Fixed an issue that it Can't Boot from bootable DVD.&Fixed an issue that Fn+F2/F3 will get stuck when repeating to press in linux.

a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Name: ThinkPad X13/T14s Gen 1 AMD
a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Summary: Lenovo ThinkPad X13/T14s Gen 1 AMD System Firmware
a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Description: Lenovo ThinkPad X13/T14s Gen 1 AMD System Firmware.

a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Name: ThinkPad X13/T14s Gen 1 AMD
a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Summary: Lenovo ThinkPad X13/T14s Gen 1 AMD System Firmware
a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Description:
This stable release fixes the following issues:

  • Included a security issue update.
  • Change the processing order of the Block SID commands.
  • Fixed an issue that Linux Fn+H/M/L keep input and touchpad hang problem.
  • Fixed an issue that No action respond after click the option by finger in BIOS/Boot menu with Touch panel SKU.
  • Fixed an issue that Enhanced Bottom Access Tamper Detection issue.

Some new functionality has also been added:

  • Add Support Shutdown Notification for NVMe SSD during BIOS update.
  • Add back flash prevention that can't rollback to older BIOS version.

a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Name: ThinkPad X13/T14s Gen 1 AMD
a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Summary: Lenovo ThinkPad X13/T14s Gen 1 AMD System Firmware
a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Description:
This stable release fixes the following issues:

  • Unit report abnormal beep code after plug out LCD cable then power on unit.
  • One dock LED is always on after system enter S3/S4/S5 and attach two same dock to system.

a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Name: ThinkPad X13/T14s Gen 1 AMD
a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Summary: Lenovo ThinkPad X13/T14s Gen 1 AMD System Firmware
a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Description:
This stable release fixes the following issues:

  • Fixed mouse test have no function in LENOVO Diagnost after shutdown.
  • Fixed system will auto wake up when putting system to S3 then close lid.
  • Fixed system auto resume from S3 after attach 45W/65W typec power adapter in S3 mode.
  • Enable smart card pre boot function.
  • Fixed GUI setup screen and small lenovo logo show overlap when click blank on BIOS setup.

Some new functionality has also been added:

  • Back flash prevention for Type11 Country code.
  • Support PI_DLS mode on MP battery.
  • Enable 802.11ax for Ukraine shipment.
  • Support SMBios release to support country code.
  • Qualify BOE low power panel on T14s AMD platform.

a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Name: ThinkPad X13/T14s Gen 1 AMD
a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Summary: Lenovo ThinkPad X13 T14s  AMD System Firmware
a45df35ac0e948ee180fe216a5f703f32dda163f.Description:
This stable release fixes the following issues:

  • Fixed an issue where BIOS has incorrect GUID in ACPI table.In case user cannot update the UEFI

BIOS later version,must update v1.25 first.

  • Truncated TCO logo at POST screen on both HD andFHD Display.
  • Update PI patch code.
  • Fixed an issue that TP&Trackpoint/Keyboard have no function after close lid during

Restart/Full shutdown/S4.

  • Fixed an issue that the POST hang up with Lindy cable.
